e":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b4bb9462061429ca75fc6e78399e9ab8e7821438","tid":652981,"uid":58223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"美國點解要和解<br />\n明明可以壓制中國經濟威脅<br />\n傾好咗嘅話咁周邊國家咪同以前一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定今次會面只係做下樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"所謂既和解，係美國迫中國減關稅，就係要加強美國產品既競爭力<br />\n<br />\n如果美國貨同中國貨只差20%價錢，心知中國貨差既中國人就會仆去買美國貨，中國貨無人買，資金外流，玩死中國公司，最後執埋，就變左中國人民幫外國公司打工。<br />\n<br />\n根本就係渣住中國個春袋，試想中國貨如果有外國貨8成質素，點會咁樣俾俾人吊住嚟打<br />\n<br />\n所以中國根本未準備好入世貿，想扮野入住先，吹水會慢慢放關稅，今次只係 trump 撩左件事出嚟"},{"pid":"de038637dd61cc17c24e476f867eaf7c0480ef75","tid":652981,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"Wiener's republic of china<br />\n<br />\n中華人民共贏國"},{"pid":"713aae9ace3b614a6163ba9ac71628ee12ca5f59","tid":652981,"uid":76310,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔公平？<br />\n你偷人野，抄人野，呃人野就公平？<br />\nWto無一項履行到，呃人呃左18年"},{"pid":"85b5fea23d8a9d5451b53b74038fe5069a36d8d8","tid":652981,"uid":182475,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"713aae9ace3b614a6163ba9ac71628ee12ca5f59","tid":652981,"uid":76310,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔公平？<br />\n你偷人野，抄人野，呃人野就公平？<br />\nWto無一項履行到，呃人呃左18年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"根本美國啲要求合理到不得了..."},{"pid":"6faab1a6d0abb8e36a6905b76ff245be62e315c4","tid":652981,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"支共d廠一間執一間  頂到幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f5bd2f965b13b784e296dbd1891e4947e14e45","tid":652981,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4bb946206142